    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have been cooking for 25 min, move them to one side of the tray and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to the other side</p><p>Top the <strong>brioche base[s]</strong> with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and put the tray[s] in the oven for a final 5 min or until the brioche halves are crusty and the cheese has melted</p>",
